# This file is intentionally kept as a template only.
# Do NOT add real production secrets or environment-specific values here.
# 
# Production configuration should be provided via your deployment platform's
# environment variables (e.g., Vercel project env vars) or an untracked
# local `.env.production` file that is not committed to git.
#
# Default Clerk URLs are already documented in `frontend/.env.example` and
# project docs. If you need a reference, you can use the commented examples
# below and copy them into your real, untracked `.env.production`:
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_URL=/sign-in
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_UP_URL=/sign-up
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_FALLBACK_REDIRECT_URL=/dashboard
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_UP_FALLBACK_REDIRECT_URL=/dashboard
